<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246451 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-4.jpg" alt="a white cardboard mailer with a monstera in a white pot" width="1411" height="1790" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-4.jpg 1411w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-4-640x812.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-4-960x1218.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-4-1211x1536.jpg 1211w" sizes="(max-width: 1411px) 100vw, 1411px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246452 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-5.jpg" alt="a white cardboard mailer with a plant in a terracotta pot" width="1501" height="1836" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-5.jpg 1501w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-5-640x783.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-5-960x1174.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-5-1256x1536.jpg 1256w" sizes="(max-width: 1501px) 100vw, 1501px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246453 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-6.jpg" alt="a white envelope with a plant in a white pot" width="1453" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-6.jpg 1453w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-6-640x846.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-6-960x1269.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-6-1162x1536.jpg 1162w" sizes="(max-width: 1453px) 100vw, 1453px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246454 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-7.jpg" alt="a USPS mailer with a plant in a terracotta pot" width="1620" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-7.jpg 1620w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-7-640x759.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-7-960x1138.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-7-1296x1536.jpg 1296w" sizes="(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px"></p>
<div id="attachment_246448" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246448" class="wp-image-246448 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-1.jpg" alt="a collection of small paintings of plants in pots on used envelopes. all are on a white gallery wall" width="1920" height="1234" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-1.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-1-640x411.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-1-960x617.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/perez-1-1536x987.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246448" class="wp-caption-text">Photo by Argenis Apolinario, courtesy pf PS122 Gallery, N.Y.</p>
</div>
